    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The LibVLC media list player plays a libvlc_media_list_t list of media, in a certain order. This is required to especially support playlist files. The normal libvlc_media_player_t LibVLC media player can only play a single media, and does not handle playlist files properly. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
